userdoc.notice: Main point of interaction with SLI Protocol This is a proof of concept starter contract for lossless insurance Aave v2 is used to generate interest from premium deposits Premium is returned to beneficiary after the PoolTracker contract controls deposit calls to Aave to make approvals needed only once per token.
